## Acknowledgments

We would like to thank the following people and organizations for their support:

### Institutions
- **Instituto Politécnico Nacional (IPN)** - Primary academic institution
- **BEIFI Program** - Research internship funding and support

### Open Source Community
- Intel RealSense team - Camera SDK and documentation
- NVIDIA - Jetson platform and CUDA support
- OpenCV contributors - Computer vision library
- Python community - Language and ecosystem
- GCC developers - C compiler

### Libraries and Tools
- pyrealsense2 - Intel RealSense Python SDK
- OpenCV - Computer vision and image processing
- NumPy - Numerical computing
- Matplotlib - Data visualization
- Jupyter - Interactive computing notebooks

### Educational Resources
- Stack Overflow community - Problem-solving assistance
- GitHub community - Code hosting and collaboration
- Academic papers and research - Theoretical foundation

## Code Attribution

Some portions of this project were inspired by or adapted from:

- Intel RealSense examples - Camera initialization and frame handling
- OpenCV tutorials - Image processing techniques
- PID control literature - Control system implementation

All adaptations have been modified to fit the specific needs of this project
and properly attributed where applicable.

